# Test Environment Variables Template

This file documents the environment variables used for integration tests.
The actual `.env.test` file is auto-generated by the test orchestrator.

## Wallet Configuration

```
# Anvil default account (10000 ETH pre-funded)
WALLET_PRIVATE_KEY=0xac0974bec39a17e36ba4a6b4d238ff944bacb476cbed5490deccb132b12c722
WALLET_ADDRESS=0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266
WALLET_ACCOUNT_INDEX=0

# Additional test accounts
TEST_ACCOUNT_2_PRIVATE_KEY=0x59c6995e998f97a5a0044966f0945389dc9e86dae88c7a8412f4603b6b78690d
TEST_ACCOUNT_2_ADDRESS=0x70997970C51812e339D9B73b0245ad39a4fcf8d4

