## Contract Addresses

These are deployed via `DeployDexesBundle.s.sol`

```
# Deployed contract addresses
DEXES_ACCESS_MANAGER=0x...
DEXES_WEB3PGP=0x...
DEXES_WEB3SIGN=0x...
```

## Network Configuration

```
# Anvil RPC endpoint
RPC_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8545

# Anvil chain ID
CHAIN_ID=31337
```

## Jest Configuration

```
# Test timeout in milliseconds
JEST_TIMEOUT=120000
```

## Notes

- All accounts are pre-funded with 10000 ETH on anvil
- Private keys are deterministic and standard anvil defaults
- `.env.test` is auto-generated by `npm test`
- `.env.test` is in `.gitignore` (not committed to repository)
